DESCRIPTION:<2026-03-05 Thu 15:00-17:30>\n:OWNER: GXG :Effort: 2:30\n1. ☐ c
 heck PEC consistency/reproducibility by using several samples\n   with 40w
 t% reline\,\n   1. do we need a rinse of the PEC with 1.0M NaCl before\n  
     dissolution tests?\n   2. ☐ set up a time-lapse video to see how much 
 mixing time is\n      needed.\n   3. decided that making "fresh" PEC is pr
 obably best for\n      dissolution studies.\n2. ☐ Giovanni needs to read a
 bout NMR for PEC dissolution before\n   contacting Weiguo.
